{"tid":635350,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IPhone SE 2 的確存在！支援雙卡雙待有希望？","createTime":"2018-04-20T05:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T06:07:16.000Z","uid":112485,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"701191695d381a513bef7ab9675eb3e72eb879bf","tid":635350,"uid":112485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"一直傳出 Apple 有意推出入門級的低價版 iPhone，如同幾年前推出 iPhone SE 一樣，不過之前一直是推測，仍未有任何比較可靠的證據來証明該機的確存在。但日前從歐亞經濟委員會的監管資料庫中出現該機的蹤影，成為最有力的證據。<br />\n<br />\n監管資料庫過往已暗示過各種新產品推出，包括 AirPods、iPhone 7、新 iPad 等，而現在從資料庫中發現全新的 iPhone ID，而且仍有一部未發表的 iPhone，而此 iPhone 極可能是 SE 2。<br />\n<br />\n要留意通常會在資料庫中出現的話，都會在近期出現，就似 HomePod 或新 iPad 一樣。除此之外，有傳新機將有雙 SIM 卡設計，不過雙 SIM 卡設計的智能手機於美國並不是很受歡迎，反而在美洲、歐洲和亞洲市場卻非常流行，如果蘋果真的發佈雙 SIM 卡設計，或可以挖掘新的客戶群。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/iphone-se-2-19042018-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fiphone-se-2-19042018-2%2F&d=wFUHqL6JyT4V6SMNQ0yoBm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f547650f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/iphone-se-2-19042018-2/</a>"},{"pid":"bcf2bf3ea3f5e15177847f68f8489660ccfd0e4b","tid":635350,"uid":112416,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"apple終於肯發明雙卡雙侍喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4258708e6e933b04ad7ccec19a00ce1d8067d2d0","tid":635350,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86541929342f7dd42d6bfb464dab78426de0c542","tid":635350,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左既話買嚟做後備機幾好"},{"pid":"63af8fb90789177d108d8ee5e4b3397dcccedaac","tid":635350,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1d358d4a9c3e18ab51e2cce919daa9da077203f","ti